description:
The Mapbox Maps plugin for Bubble provides integration with Mapbox. 

It Allows:
1. Show the map
2. Zoom/in. 
3. Go to current location.  

If you want any features, mail me at nocodetalks@gmail.com

This plugin is in development, so keep sharing feature you want to add in this plugin. Mail me at nocodetalks@gmail.com. 

Learn Bubble Plugin development - https://store.nocodetalks.co/l/bubble-plugin?layout=profile
name: Mapbox
